{"id": "art-16", "label": "Art. 16", "title": "Art. 16", "slug": "art-16", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 16 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Aporturile\nîn numerar sunt obligatorii la constituirea oric&#259;rei forme de societate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_990765885\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2502\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_990765885\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Aporturile în natur&#259; trebuie s&#259; fie evaluabile\ndin punct de vedere economic. Ele sunt admise la toate formele de societate <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sunt v&#259;rsate prin transferarea drepturilor\ncorespunz&#259;toare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prin predarea\nefectiv&#259; c&#259;tre societate a bunurilor aflate în stare de utilizare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1422722663\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2501\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1422722663\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Aporturile în <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;e</span> au\nregimul juridic al aporturilor în natur&#259;, nefiind admise la <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\ncare se constituie prin <span class=SpellE>subscrip&#355;ie</span> public&#259;\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nici la <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nîn comandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> cu r&#259;spundere\nlimitat&#259;. Aporturile în <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;e</span> sunt\nliberate, potrivit art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>84</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_402348825\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2500\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_402348825\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Presta&#355;iile</span> în munc&#259;\nsau servicii nu pot constitui aport la formarea ori la majorarea capitalului\nsocial.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span>\nîn societatea în nume colectiv <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>comandita&#355;i</span>\nse pot obliga la <span class=SpellE>presta&#355;ii</span> în munc&#259; cu\ntitlu de aport social, dar care nu pot constitui aport la formarea sau la\nmajorarea capitalului social. În schimbul acestui aport, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nau dreptul s&#259; participe, potrivit actului constitutiv, la <span\nclass=SpellE>împ&#259;r&#355;irea</span> beneficiilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na activului social, r&#259;mânând, totodat&#259;, <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span>\ns&#259; participe la pierderi.</span></p>"}